title: Dodgers' Ethier yells at Mattingly in dugout
text:
> Sports Dodgers' Ethier yells at Mattingly in dugout Los Angeles Dodgers manager Don Mattingly, left, and New York Mets manager Terry Collins, right, talk during batting practice before the Los Angeles Dodgers play the New York Mets in Game 5 of baseball's National League Division Series Thursday, Oct. 15, 2015, in Los Angeles. (AP Photo/Lenny Ignelzi)
